data.title: Japanese Restaurant
data.meta_description: Japanese restaurant. Special appetizers. Sushi. Bento boxes. Gluten-free menu. Takeout available. Serving for over 20 years. Call for reservations.
data.text:
Authentic Japanese Dishes

JMK Nippon specializes in serving the best Japanese dishes. We're a local Japanese restaurant that has established a name for itself in Rockford, IL. We have been serving delicious food in a warm, inviting atmosphere for over 20 years. Call for reservations.

Treat Yourself to Our Teppan Dishes

JMK Nippon is a local, family-owned restaurant specializing in authentic Japanese dishes. Our delicious dishes are sure to satisfy your appetite. We also have gluten-free options for your benefit.

Salads and Entrees

From salads and noodle soups to yakisoba, we have it all. Feast on your favorite dishes or try something new. Our staff is more than happy to help you choose a tasty dish.

Have a Hearty Lunch

Enjoy a delicious meal with your entire family at our restaurant. Our kids' menu and senior citizen's menu ensure that we have something for everybody. Visit us today for tasty Japanese food!

A Wide Variety of Sushi

If you're a sushi lover, then JMK Nippon is the place for you. We have a wide variety of sushi options from shrimp to tuna to eel. Call us for reservations today.

Try Special Appetizers

Start your meal with our tasty appetizers. From delicious calamari to exotic shrimp cocktail, we have great options. So come to JMK Nippon and treat your taste buds.

Extras and Sides

JMK Nippon is your ideal spot for a quick bite to eat. Choose from a variety of food menu options like our hibachi vegetables, noodles, rice, and more. Call us today for reservations.
